<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王室准备了一艘船送王子去邻国。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一艘华丽的船做好了出发的准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子对小美人鱼解释这次航海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我父母的希望，他们希望我见见那个公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，你我都知道，我不会跟她结婚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毕竟，她不是救我命的那个女孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼又一次想：“王子不知道是我救了他，真让人伤心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，如果除了梅丹，我不得不选另一位新娘，” 王子继续说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那会是你。” 然后，他像哥哥一样亲了亲小美人鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼抬头对着他微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许最后，我会跟王子结婚的。” 她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那一刻，她很幸福。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想请求你跟我一起去这次航海，我的小伙伴。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望你不会害怕大海。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼微笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王子不知道，其实大海就是我的家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼跟着王子登上船，开始了航海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个晚上，当大家都睡着了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼坐在甲板上，呆呆地望着大海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她觉得自己看见她的家人都在海面上，他们好像在叫她回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望你们过得好。” 她想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我必须跟着我的心走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，船开进了附近王国的港口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里的国王和王后在等着王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>高塔上传来了喇叭声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个国家的国民们都聚在码头欢迎他们的宾客。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他很帅！” 一个女孩儿一看见王子走下船，就喊起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“和我们公主太般配了。” 一个老太太说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她没能来迎接他，太可惜了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“公主明天会到这儿来。” 那个女孩儿回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让他等一下没关系的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，所有人都在街上庆祝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，王室卫兵骑马过来宣布：“到王宫大厅来！公主到了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都来到大厅。他们想好好儿看看公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼也很好奇，她拨开了人群。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，公主出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她高高的，很优雅，穿着白色的连衣裙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她真的很漂亮。” 小美人鱼想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她看起来还很眼熟。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主的皮肤白皙、透明。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她黑色的头发又长又亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她长长的深色睫毛下，有一双深绿的眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼想：“王子对跟她结婚不感兴趣，我很开心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，就在这时，王子走过去迎接公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他在近处看公主时，他大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是你！是你救了我的命。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我记得我在海边醒过来时，看见过你的脸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他牵起梅丹的小手，大胆地亲了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能再见到你，我真幸运，我的公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>能和你结婚，我太荣幸了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>